title: November Trade Talk: Doing Business in India (North Dakota Trade Office)
text: ( Source : North Dakota Trade Office ) Join us on Wednesday, November 4 as we welcome the Consul General of India , Dr. Ausaf Sayeed, to North Dakota. Dr. Sayeed, along with Consul ( Commerce ) D.B. Bhati , will discuss U.S. -India trade relations
